issue.title: [document] 案例收集 - 非游戏内容
issue.body:
## detail | 详细描述
PuerTS除了用于游戏业务之外，还可以用于非游戏业务开发。不仅是Unity/UE里的非游戏业务，也可以是一个dotnet项目（Puer Unity的单元测试就是dotnet程序）

PuerTS的文档也希望展示一些非游戏内容开发的经验，欢迎社区的朋友来分享相关案例。

-----

PuerTS can not only be used in game development. you can also use it in app development such as dotnet program.

PuerTS document needs to show some experience that is being used in app development. Sharing is welcomed.
